wminc-desc: Si̱tem wuki mak da̱nian A̱vwuogo Wukimedia
wminc-prefinfo-language: A̱lyem tsi̱tsak ang ka - ka̱ vwuon ma̱ng wuki mak ang hu
wminc-prefinfo-code: Zwunzwuo-a̱muup ISO 639 a̱lyem ji nang a nyian ta̱m tazwa a̱ji
wminc-prefinfo-project: Khai  ta̱m Wukimedia hu nang a nyian ta̱m tazwa nhu a̱ji
wminc-prefinfo-error: A khai ta̱m ghyang ku cat zwunzwuo-a̱muup a̱lyem a̱ni.
wminc-error-move-unprefixed: Ghyuap: Wat hu nang a kwan shyei a̱ nat [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|a̱ni nwai byia̱ zwunzwuo-a̱zama ku a tyia̱ zwunzwuo-a̱zama ji̱ nwai tyia̱ a̱ni]].
wminc-error-wronglangcode: Ghyuap: Wat huni byia̱ [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|zwunzwuo-a̱muup a̱lyem ji̱ nwai tyia̱ a̱ni]] "$1".
wminc-error-unprefixed-suggest: Ghyuap: Wat huni [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|nwai byia̱ zwunzwuo-a̱zama]]! A maai a khwuk wat ghyang mi̱ [[:$1]].
wminc-error-wiki-exists: Wuki huni wa ka̱n nshyia̱. A maai a cat wat huni da̱ $1. Ka̱ ku nwai labeang neet nang á̱ nkhwuk wuki hu, da̱ ma̱sa̱kut ya nfwuong áwa ku mmam ma̱ a̱da̱dei si̱ nang a̱mgba̱m nkyangmami na ku nwuo.
wminc-error-wiki-sister: Wat huni yet kap ta̱m hwa ku bu nwai shyia̱ a̱ji a̱ni. Ma̱sa̱kut nat ma̱ $1 a cat wuki hu.
wminc-viewuserlang: Nwuan a̱lyem a̱tyunta̱m ka ma̱ng wuki mak hu a li
wminc-ip: "$1" yet a̱vwuonswat IP kya ku a̱tyunta̱m kicong wa.
action-viewuserlang: nwuan a̱lyem a̱tyunta̱m ka ma̱ng wuki mak hu a li
right-viewuserlang: Nwuan a̱lyem a̱tyunta̱m ka ma̱ng wuki mak hu a li
wminc-listusers-testwiki: A shyia̱ di̱ nwuan á̱nietnta̱m ba̱ ku tyia̱ kyangcatlan wuki mak mba hu di̱ $1.
wminc-search-nocreate-nopref: A ku nzop "$1". Ma̱sa̱kut tyia̱ [[Special:Preferences|kyangcatlan wuki mak]] ang hu zi̱ ka tak ma̱ng a̱nwan zang wat hwa a maai a khwuk!
wminc-searchwiki-noresults: Záng nwai nshyia̱. A maai a nzop di̱n vak zwunzwuo-a̱muup a̱lyem, lyulyoot mbyin ma̱ng lyulyoot di̱ tyannwuan a̱lyem ang ji ku di̱n Shong.
wminc-searchwiki-match-nativename: "$1" wa yet a̱lyoot $2 da̱ a̱lyem a̱kya.
wminc-infopage-welcome: Ma̱ aba̱n/Tyebaa ang ma̱ng bai A̱vwuogo Wukimedia ka, ta̱m Sotbeang Wukimedia ([[{{MediaWiki:Aboutpage}}|Tazwa]])
wminc-infopage-missingwiki-text: $1 ghyang da̱ a̱lyem kani nshyia̱ bah.
wminc-infopage-option-sisterprojects-exi: A maai a nzop nta̱m na̱ wa ka̱n nshyia̱ a̱ni da̱ a̱lyem kani:
wminc-infopage-option-sisterprojects-oth: A maai a nzop nta̱m jhyang da̱ a̱lyem kani:
wminc-infopage-option-multilingual: Ku, a maai a nat di̱ wuki lilyem ma a̱di̱di̱t:
wminc-infopage-createmainpage: Nwuo ma̱ng swang a̱lyiat ji "A̱tsak Wat" da̱ a̱lyem kani:
wminc-infopage-contribute: Ka̱nang a lyen a̱lyem kani, á̱ tyei ang gba̱gbak a nwuo jhyet!
wminc-infopage-status-open: Si̱ huni yet a̱gang wuki A̱vwuogo Wukimedia wa.
wminc-infopage-status-imported: Wuki A̱vwuogo hu ku byia̱ a̱ nwuo neet mi̱ $1 wa nang á̱ sii du nyim nggu.
wminc-infopage-error: Ghyuap: a maai nyia̱ ta̱m ma̱ng {{#infopage}} di̱ ngwat na̱ byia̱ zwunzwuo-a̱zama ja ma̱nyin.
